    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Professor Sophie Witter (BA, MA, PhD) is a Professor of International Health Financing and Health Systems in the Institute for Global Health and Development Division at Queen Margaret University, Edinburgh. Sophie is also a member of the Institute for Global Health and Development Research Centre. <br /><br /><br /></p>]]></Value>
